{"tid":1380370,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國歌，作為香港人依定要唱","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:52:03.000Z","uid":226728,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1082392120466b4a0d8eef192550f031742125","tid":1380370,"uid":226728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"（我係打錯個「<span style=\"color: red;\">一</span>」字引你地入黎睇的）<br />\n<br />\n田漢當年填詞真係不得了，一詞多意。<br />\n紅綠兩句中間有停頓位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家試下用香港人身份代入去唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />向前線人員致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起來！<br />\n不願做奴隸的人們！<br />\n把我們的血肉<br />\n築成我們新的長城！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中華民族到了</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">最危險的時候</span><br />\n<br />\n每個人被迫着發出最後的吼聲。<br />\n起來！起來！起來！<br />\n我們萬眾一心，<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！<br />\n前進！前進！進！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c0cbe7af3f4119dfdccf6f2b22ca94fa8e689e25","tid":1380370,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:07:50.000Z","msg":"香港有否國歌？"},{"pid":"180a2be25a619a8a164389b682e28e293e2e1bfe","tid":1380370,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:08:54.000Z","msg":"今天我"},{"pid":"d4a86bdb1ad95254d38c96873824db6d296d3930","tid":1380370,"uid":156632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:09:01.000Z","msg":"今日3pm港澳辦開記招 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今日一定好多水軍洗版帶風向想分化各位手足<br />\n呢場運動之所以仲繼續到落去全賴大家學識不割蓆 所以唔好被輕易帶動<br />\n邊個話袋住先就屌鳩佢老母<br />\n遇到啲講錯嘢嘅手足要予以糾正 以防更多人受影響<br />\n</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n遇到三毛 上一頁 唔好推唔好負評有佢沉 <br />\n三毛特癥：<br />\n-禁入個po冇內容可言/得幾隻字<br />\n-標題黨<br />\n-p牌<br />\n<br />\n死左咁多、拉左咁多義士要我地算數？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路走來咁辛苦唔好輕易退讓 <br />\n我地要一齊實現五大訴求加清算警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n有關聽日港澳辦開會事情，大家聽我講講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆不篤灰只係理念唔係絕對 唔好俾呢樣嘢騎劫！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"23ab04534adc6ba30b2dfbda37990ebc5f47d16b","tid":1380370,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0cbe7af3f4119dfdccf6f2b22ca94fa8e689e25","tid":1380370,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:07:50.000Z","msg":"香港有否國歌？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"do you hear the people sing"},{"pid":"ca9d30682cd493d224a4087c4ab550c12f47ca13","tid":1380370,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ab04534adc6ba30b2dfbda37990ebc5f47d16b","tid":1380370,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0cbe7af3f4119dfdccf6f2b22ca94fa8e689e25","tid":1380370,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:07:50.000Z","msg":"香港有否國歌？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"do you hear the people sing"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"今天我"},{"pid":"cd016d09a55ec36b972fe4852f7c198aa0907356","tid":1380370,"uid":257864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca9d30682cd493d224a4087c4ab550c12f47ca13","tid":1380370,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ab04534adc6ba30b2dfbda37990ebc5f47d16b","tid":1380370,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0cbe7af3f4119dfdccf6f2b22ca94fa8e689e25","tid":1380370,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply